# API & Core Changes Required for Mobile Canvas Workflow Builder

## Overview

The mobile canvas is not just a UI. It requires new API endpoints, new core data models, new execution logic, and extensions to existing systems. Here's everything that needs to change, layer by layer.

---

## Part 1: Database Schema Changes

### 1.1 New Tables

```sql
-- ============================================
-- WORKFLOW DEFINITION (Canvas + Template)
-- ============================================

CREATE TABLE workflow_definitions (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    owner_user_id UUID NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id),
    project_id UUID REFERENCES projects(id),
    
